'''NMNAT1'''是'''[[烟酰胺|烟酰胺]]单核苷酸腺苷转移酶1'''，是[[烟酰胺腺嘌呤二核苷酸|烟酰胺腺嘌呤二核苷酸]]生物合成中一种关键的[[酶|酶]]，在人类中由''NMNAT1''[[基因|基因]]编码<ref name="genecard">{{cite web| title = GeneCards: NMNAT1 nicotinamide nucleotide adenylyltransferase 1| url = http://www.genecards.org/cgi-bin/carddisp.pl?gene=NMNAT1| accessdate = 2013-08-30| archive-date = 2013-08-16| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130816221734/http://genecards.org/cgi-bin/carddisp.pl?gene=NMNAT1| dead-url = no}}</ref>。除了[[脾脏|脾脏]]，NMNAT1在人体其他[[组织|组织]][[器官|器官]]中均有表达<ref name="tissue">{{cite journal |author= Zhai RG, Rizzi M, Garavaglia S.|title= Nicotinamide/nicotinic acid mononucleotide adenylyltransferase, new insights into an ancient enzyme |journal= Cell Mol Life Sci. |volume= 66|issue= 17|pages= 2805-18|pmid= 19448972 |date=Sep 2009}}</ref>。小鼠中''NMNAT1''基因的缺失导致胚胎期死亡<ref name="knockout">{{cite journal |author= Conforti L, Janeckova L, Wagner D, Mazzola F, Cialabrini L, Di Stefano M, Orsomando G, Magni G, Bendotti C, Smyth N, Coleman M.|title= Reducing expression of NAD+ synthesizing enzyme NMNAT1 does not affect the rate of Wallerian degeneration |journal= FEBS J.|volume= 278|issue= 15|pages= 2666-79|pmid= 21615689 |date=Aug 2011}}</ref>。

''NMNAT1''基因的[[突变|突变]]可导致[[莱伯先天性黑蒙症|莱伯先天性黑蒙症]]。一些患者具有特异性的[[黄斑|黄斑]]退化症状。<ref name="pmid22842230">{{cite journal | author = Koenekoop RK, Wang H, Majewski J, Wang X, Lopez I, Ren H, Chen Y, Li Y, Fishman GA, Genead M, Schwartzentruber J, Solanki N, Traboulsi EI, Cheng J, Logan CV, McKibbin M, Hayward BE, Parry DA, Johnson CA, Nageeb M, Poulter JA, Mohamed MD, Jafri H, Rashid Y, Taylor GR, Keser V, Mardon G, Xu H, Inglehearn CF, Fu Q, Toomes C, Chen R, Finding of Rare Disease Genes (FORGE) Canada, Consortium | title = Mutations in NMNAT1 cause Leber congenital amaurosis and identify a new disease pathway for retinal degeneration | journal = Nat. Genet. | volume = 44 | issue = 9 | pages = 1035–9 | pmid = 22842230 | pmc = 3657614 | doi = 10.1038/ng.2356 |date=September 2012}}</ref>

